header.gameNote: WEST COAST CONFERENCE MEN'S TOURNAMENT - FINAL

videos.description: In transition,  Johnathan Williams obliterates the rim with a powerful one-handed slam that gets the bench off its feet.
videos.headline: Williams throws down monster slam early on for the Zags

videos.description: Nigel Wiliams-Goss finds the cutting Silas Melson who slams one in for the Zags.
videos.headline: Gonzaga's Melson flies high for the jam

videos.description: In transition, Jordan Mathews gives to Przemek Karnowski for the score. Then, Nigel Williams-Goss goes coast-to-coast spinning and laying it in.
videos.headline: Gonzaga scoring with ease on the break

videos.description: Nigel Williams-Goss gets the steal and then goes coast-to-coast for the layup plus the foul.
videos.headline: Defense leads to offense for Zags' Williams-Goss

videos.description: Gonzaga head coach Mark Few on his team's success in the first half.
videos.headline: Few: "We've been in attack mode all night"

videos.description: Emmett Naar sees Joe Rahon all alone at the wing and drains the 3-pointer for Saint Mary's.
videos.headline: Saint Mary's Naar with the nice dime leading to wide-open 3-pointer

videos.description: Gonzaga's Josh Perkins drives and gives Johnathan Williams a great feed then Williams does the rest with a two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Williams dunks off a great Perkins pass for Gonzaga

videos.description: Jock Landale gets his defender in the air and makes the layup, then gets the block on the other end for Saint Mary's.
videos.headline: Saint Mary's Landale carrying the team on his back

videos.description: Gonzaga's Przemek Karnowski draws contact but is still able to finish the lay-in through 3 St. Mary's defenders.
videos.headline: Karnowski scores and draws foul through 3 St. Mary's defenders

videos.description: Nigel Williams-Goss goes coast-to-coast and then gets the floater to go plus the foul for Gonzaga.
videos.headline: Zags' Williams-Goss muscles his way for the and-1 floater

videos.description: Gonzaga defeats St. Mary's 74-56 en route to their 5th straight West Coast Championship
videos.headline: Gonzaga wins the West Coast Championship

videos.description: Gonzaga's Przemek Karnowski talks about ignoring those who doubt Gonzaga and focusing on their team.
videos.headline: Karnowski on Gonzaga's success this season

videos.description: Johnathan Williams explains how his team just competed today to get the win over Saint Mary's.
videos.headline: Zags'  Williams talks about how his team played tonight

videos.description: Jeff Goodman joins Scott Van Pelt to discuss Gonzaga's performance against Saint Mary's and why Mark Few doesn't care about a No. 1 seed.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Analysis (Goodman still has questions for Gonzaga) 2017/03/07 ESHEET SC SVP
